{"tid":2368592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓將目前防疫措施再延長兩周 放寬部分設施防疫要求","createTime":"2021-01-16T10:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T15:15:46.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb700b22c3c55ed28b284c666e7ef954a909dd4","tid":2368592,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"南韓將目前防疫措施再延長兩周 放寬部分設施防疫要求<br />\n2021-01-16 HKT 16:26<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......南韓防疫部門宣布，將現行防疫措施及禁止5人以上聚會的規定再延長兩星期，直至今個月31日，並將下月1日至14日，定為「春節特別防疫期」......<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">政府決定有條件放寬部分設施的防疫要求，咖啡廳晚上9時前可提供堂食</span>，滑雪場內的餐廳和咖啡廳亦可以重新營業。<span class=\"red\">首都圈的室內體育設施及練歌廳獲准重開，限制是每8平方米1人。</span> &quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570767-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570767-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyO6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=73a810c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570767-20210116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=999d1dd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570767-20210116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"blue\">有點兒羨慕南韓</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a48692cbe61b2f099525cfb215119b1cd32498b4","tid":2368592,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"push"}]}